# Design System Rules

## Figma Token → Tailwind Mapping

When implementing designs from Figma, map design tokens as follows:

### Colors
- Map Figma color tokens to CSS variables defined in `src/styles/globals.css`
- Primary colors → `bg-primary`, `text-primary`, `border-primary`
- Secondary colors → `bg-secondary`, `text-secondary`
- Background → `bg-background`, `bg-card`, `bg-muted`
- Text → `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`
- Borders → `border`, `border-input`
- If the Figma design uses custom colors not in the theme, add them as CSS variables in globals.css under `:root` and `.dark`

### Typography
- Map Figma text styles to Tailwind classes
- Use `font-sans` (Inter) for body text and `font-mono` (JetBrains Mono) for code
- Headings: `text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight` (h1), `text-3xl font-bold` (h2), `text-2xl font-semibold` (h3)
- Body: `text-base` (16px), `text-sm` (14px), `text-xs` (12px)
- Leading: `leading-tight` (1.25), `leading-normal` (1.5), `leading-relaxed` (1.625)

### Spacing
- 4px grid system: `p-1` (4px), `p-2` (8px), `p-3` (12px), `p-4` (16px), `p-6` (24px), `p-8` (32px)
- Section spacing: `py-12` (48px) to `py-20` (80px)
- Component gaps: `gap-4` (16px), `gap-6` (24px), `gap-8` (32px)

### Border Radius
- Map Figma radius to `--radius` variable: `rounded-sm`, `rounded-md`, `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`
- Default component radius is `rounded-lg` (var(--radius))

### Shadows
- Subtle: `shadow-sm`
- Default: `shadow`
- Elevated: `shadow-md`
- High: `shadow-lg`

## Component Mapping (shadcn/ui)

When Figma has UI components, prefer shadcn/ui equivalents:
- Buttons → `@/components/ui/button`
- Input fields → `@/components/ui/input`
- Dropdowns → `@/components/ui/select` or `@/components/ui/dropdown-menu`
- Modals → `@/components/ui/dialog`
- Cards → `@/components/ui/card`
- Tabs → `@/components/ui/tabs`
- Navigation → `@/components/ui/navigation-menu`
- Mobile menu → `@/components/ui/sheet`
- Toast/alerts → `sonner`

## Custom Components

When Figma UI kit has components not covered by shadcn/ui:
1. Create in `src/components/custom/`
2. Follow shadcn/ui conventions: use CVA for variants, cn() for className merging
3. Use Tailwind CSS variables for theming (not hardcoded colors)
4. Include both light and dark mode styles
5. Make responsive by default (mobile-first)

## Responsive Breakpoints
- Mobile: default (< 640px)
- Tablet: `sm:` (640px), `md:` (768px)
- Desktop: `lg:` (1024px), `xl:` (1280px), `2xl:` (1536px)
